WEBVTT

30:35.700 --> 30:36.530 line:80%
Changyu,

30:37.380 --> 30:40.150 line:80%
your husband writes really nice couplets—

30:40.250 --> 30:42.890 line:80%
even better than the ones Scholar Song

30:42.920 --> 30:44.290 line:80%
wrote in previous years.

30:44.290 --> 30:45.460 line:80%
That's why I say

30:45.460 --> 30:47.420 line:80%
our Changyu has good taste.
